#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "<h2 id=\"troubleshooting\">Troubleshooting</h2>\n"
msgid "<h2 id=\"troubleshoot-start\">Troubleshoot Tails not starting</h2>\n"
msgstr "<h2 id=\"troubleshooting\">Решение проблем</h2>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<ul>\n"
msgstr "<ul>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "<li>\n"
#| "<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">If your USB stick is listed in the Boot Menu but the Boot Loader does not appear, or if Tails fails to start after the Boot Loader:</p>\n"
#| "<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">If your USB stick appears in the list of startup disks but the Boot Loader does not appear, or if Tails fails to start after the Boot Loader:</p>\n"
msgid ""
"<li class=\"windows upgrade-windows\">\n"
"<p>If the computer doesn't restart on your Tails USB stick:</p>\n"
"  <ol>\n"
"    <li><p>Wait 2&ndash;3 minutes and try again. Some USB sticks need some rest after installing.</p></li>\n"
"    <li><p>Try other options in the <b>Use a device</b> screen, for example <b>USB FDD</b> if available.</p></li>\n"
"    <li><p>Try all other USB ports on the computer. Some USB ports cannot be used to start from.</p></li>\n"
"    <li><p>Refer to the [[instructions on starting Tails using the Boot Menu key|doc/first_steps/start/pc#boot-menu-key]].</p></li>\n"
"  </ol>\n"
"</li>\n"
msgstr ""
"<li>\n"
"<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">Если ваша флешка есть в загрузочном меню, но загрузка недоступна, или если Tails оказывается невозможно запустить после загрузчика:</p>\n"
"<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">Если ваша флешка есть в загрузочном меню, но загрузка недоступна, или если Tails оказывается невозможно запустить после загрузчика:</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "<li class=\"linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">\n"
#| "<p>If none of the possible Boot Menu keys from the previous technique work, or\n"
#| "if your USB stick is not listed in the Boot Menu, refer to the\n"
#| "[[troubleshooting instructions about Tails not starting at\n"
#| "all|doc/first_steps/start/pc#not-at-all]].</p>\n"
#| "</li>\n"
msgid ""
"<li class=\"linux expert pc-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">\n"
"<p>If none of the possible Boot Menu keys from the previous technique work,\n"
"refer to the [[troubleshooting instructions about Tails not starting at\n"
"all|doc/first_steps/start/pc#not-at-all]].</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
msgstr ""
"<li class=\"linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">\n"
"<p>Если не срабатывает ни одна клавиша для вызова загрузочного меню или вашей флешки нет в загрузочном меню, обратитесь к [[советам по решению проблем с загрузкой Tails|doc/first_steps/start/pc#not-at-all]].</p>\n"
"</li>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "<li>\n"
#| "<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">If your USB stick is listed in the Boot Menu but the Boot Loader does not appear, or if Tails fails to start after the Boot Loader:</p>\n"
#| "<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">If your USB stick appears in the list of startup disks but the Boot Loader does not appear, or if Tails fails to start after the Boot Loader:</p>\n"
msgid ""
"<li class=\"linux expert pc-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">\n"
"<p>If the Boot Menu appears, but your USB stick is not listed in the Boot Menu:</p>\n"
"  <ol>\n"
"  <li><p>Wait 2&ndash;3 minutes and try again. Some USB sticks need some rest after installing.</p></li>\n"
"  <li><p>Try all other USB ports on the computer. Some USB ports cannot be used to start from.</p></li>\n"
"  </ol>\n"
"</li>\n"
msgstr ""
"<li>\n"
"<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">Если ваша флешка есть в загрузочном меню, но загрузка недоступна, или если Tails оказывается невозможно запустить после загрузчика:</p>\n"
"<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">Если ваша флешка есть в загрузочном меню, но загрузка недоступна, или если Tails оказывается невозможно запустить после загрузчика:</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "<li>\n"
#| "<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">If your USB stick is listed in the Boot Menu but the Boot Loader does not appear, or if Tails fails to start after the Boot Loader:</p>\n"
#| "<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">If your USB stick appears in the list of startup disks but the Boot Loader does not appear, or if Tails fails to start after the Boot Loader:</p>\n"
msgid ""
"<li>\n"
"<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows\">If the computer restarts on your Tails USB stick, but the Boot Loader doesn't appear:</p>\n"
"<p class=\"linux expert pc-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">If your USB stick is listed in the Boot Menu, but the Boot Loader doesn't appear:</p>\n"
"<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">If your USB stick appears in the list of startup disks, but the Boot Loader doesn't appear:</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<li>\n"
"<p class=\"windows upgrade-windows linux expert install-clone upgrade-clone upgrade-tails upgrade-linux\">Если ваша флешка есть в загрузочном меню, но загрузка недоступна, или если Tails оказывается невозможно запустить после загрузчика:</p>\n"
"<p class=\"mac mac-clone upgrade-mac\">Если ваша флешка есть в загрузочном меню, но загрузка недоступна, или если Tails оказывается невозможно запустить после загрузчика:</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!inline pages=\"install/inc/steps/basic_troubleshooting.inline\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!inline pages=\"install/inc/steps/basic_troubleshooting.inline.ru\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>If your computer still does not display the Boot Loader, it might currently be impossible to start Tails on your computer.</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Если ваш компьютер не показывает загрузчик, в настоящее время может быть невозможно запустить Tails с этого компьютера.</p>\n"
"</li>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
